import json from pymongo import MongoClient
# Connexion à la base MongoDB mongodb://mongo:27017/ client = MongoClient('mongodb://mongo:27017/') db = client['test_Data354'] collection = db['last']
# Récupérer le dernier timestamp last_timestamp_doc = collection.find_one({"_id": "last_timestamp"}) last_timestamp = last_timestamp_doc.get("timestamp", "1970-01-01 00:00:00")
# Transmettre le timestamp au FlowFile flowFile = session.get() if flowFile: flowFile = session.write(flowFile, lambda out: out.write(last_timestamp.encode('utf-8'))) session.transfer(flowFile, REL_SUCCESS) else: session.transfer(flowFile, REL_FAILURE)
